	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd like to push a very picky recommendation that the anti-aliased text from the Vol. 1 title screen be nixed. Compared to all the sharp, designed-for-crisp-pixels text elsewhere, it ends up looking fuzzy and hasty, even if it represents a technologically more modern way of rendering text.<br /><br />How long do we have to tidy up our games for the cartridge release?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
